{"tid":1057412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那產汽車疑用毒材料 六車主罹患白血病","createTime":"2019-03-12T01:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T06:15:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"095650c9114bd206692a2806abb8d19dd0d4c5f3","tid":1057412,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:05:42.000Z","msg":"中國大陸國產汽車被指使用有毒材料，導致車主患病。3月9號，6名受害車主在網上發表文章舉報，說他們購買中共國企一汽大眾生產的國產化奧迪汽車後，都患上白血病或其他嚴重疾病，他們認為患病的原因，是一汽大眾生產的奧迪車內裝飾，使用了有毒材料。<br />\n <br />\n據「自由亞洲電臺」報導，一名姓林患者說，他們購買的國產奧迪，車內有異味，患病後有人把車砸了，從裡面扒拉出來二、三十斤瀝青。"},{"pid":"2a07fb69ead6fcb09dacc6c6130884d90ca1741e","tid":1057412,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無link<br />\n想分享"},{"pid":"2f7fe93fcbff24478cec33887f5f73cfebb51200","tid":1057412,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"國企一汽大眾生產的國產化奧迪汽車<br />\n<br />\n無知一問, 一汽個汽量詞嚟?"},{"pid":"e553a17ca9cb41544a37351e65af229e8e806dec","tid":1057412,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"瀝青有咩用？"},{"pid":"25cb77f761ea5f12a77ee45af66b1c85527c3da1","tid":1057412,"uid":96833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f7fe93fcbff24478cec33887f5f73cfebb51200","tid":1057412,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"國企一汽大眾生產的國產化奧迪汽車<br />\n<br />\n無知一問, 一汽個汽量詞嚟?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"公司名呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aada84efdb1619a4aee77796cac2694349ff8f39","tid":1057412,"uid":125380,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2f7fe93fcbff24478cec33887f5f73cfebb51200","tid":1057412,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"國企一汽大眾生產的國產化奧迪汽車<br />\n<br />\n無知一問, 一汽個汽量詞嚟?