re形式投資"},{"pid":"aa54c11ca629d8620826b577879f455ff212a7b7","tid":1057412,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/03/12/887129.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F887129.html&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Apem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=4f3bb84f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/03/12/887129.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9431aea1aa6fce2f48bea8a1a2c37f9d00060107","tid":1057412,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d09d407c9cce4a69d44c4b80ce1e09edba429a8","tid":1057412,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:19:29.000Z","msg":"據悉，2010年國企一汽大眾在市場上推出國產化奧迪Q5，銷售量不錯。2013年央視315特別節目《豪車裡的怪味》揭開了奧迪車導致人患白血病的緣由：奧迪車的異味來源之一是一汽大眾使用了瀝青充當阻尼片。<br />\n<br />\n瀝青能釋放苯、苯並吡等有毒氣體，長期低劑量地吸入有毒氣體會造成車主不同程度的化學中毒，包括鼻炎、皮膚病、肺病、胎兒流產或畸形等，再發展下去就是白血病等癌症。<br />\n<br />\n天津大學材料科學與工程學院一位不願意具名的教授向21世紀網透露，阻尼片是一種阻尼材料製成的薄片，使用在車輛鈑金上面，主要是為了減少噪聲、減少震動的作用。<br />\n<br />\n另一位不願透露名字的阻尼材料公司銷售人員表示，其所在公司是國內最大的汽車用阻尼材料生產企業之一，瀝青阻尼片產能達20,000噸。"},{"pid":"aa1b788267281bf47bddc0395c5f6445fced7dc2","tid":1057412,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"你係咪中國人！？你係咪中國人！？"},{"pid":"3aa39007bb441f749d67596b86cd2e2be039fcaa","tid":1057412,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"新招解決貧富懸殊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376e230520287f165c6f0824a4d7ef8d7236dcc8","tid":1057412,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"Audi係時候要考慮停止同支那合作"},{"pid":"f3012e38d4d1b71af975d64f62c889c79c489803","tid":1057412,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"毒車毀中產<br />\n疫苗滅小童<br />\n中國仲有無未來？"},{"pid":"6a696165538d48e20ac80063969e05f4c75ab040","tid":1057412,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3012e38d4d1b71af975d64f62c889c79c489803","tid":1057412,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"毒車毀中產<br />\n疫苗滅小童<br />\n中國仲有無未來？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"領導全家攞歐美護照，未來一片光明"}]}